name: EastAsianDollLikeness
description:
This is my first Lora, please be nice and forgiving for any mishaps.

EastAsiaDollLikeness_V5

What's difference ?

Main difference within korean, Japanese, Taiwan Doll Likeness is this one produces a East Asian baby faces or round faces.

Inspired by Doll Likeness created by various masters, I wanted to make a beautiful East Asian face. Since I have a soft spot for cute types such as baby faces and East Asian round faces, So I decided to make a Lora to mimic this face shape.

Having tried 3 versions before, all were unsatisfactory, and this model is by no means perfect, but it certainly has something that I find very attractive.

Please try and share and reply your results or give suggestions.

In the future, I will continue to try to make a better Lora.

support me on my patreon, help me upgrade Hardware for trainning and testing more models. Or buy me a coffee. thanks~

Tips:

• It is recommended to use (oval face) in the prompt, the effect of pinching the face of Lora will be better, and it will not produce a baby fat face.

• Also works great with other Doll Likenesses like Korean or Japanese.

• This model works best in ChilloutMix

For V5:

• The best result of using this Lora alone is around 0.4~0.85. Below 0.4 it is easy to become a mixed race or a foreign face (you can also try it if you prefer mixed race).

For V4:

• The best result of using this Lora alone is around 0.7~1.0. Below 0.6 it is easy to become a mixed race or a foreign face (you can also try it if you prefer mixed race).

Disclaimer:

As the author, I regret to inform you that the LORA model is not intended for commercial use. This decision has been made in order to prevent any potential controversies or legal issues related to impersonation or defamation that may arise from the use of the model for commercial purposes. Furthermore, allowing commercial use of the model may have a negative impact on the development of the AI community. Therefore, I strongly advise against any commercial usage of the LORA model.
